metadata.name: With Pleasure - JeffJag
metadata.description:
With Pleasure started as a generative adversarial network (GAN) image.  
I used words like Diamond, Cracked, Crystals, and Refraction to generate the base as a starting point for this hand made digital painting.

I painted over it in Procreate.  
I stretched it from rectangle to square and liquified it, then painted more.  
I increased the resolution using Topaz  Gigapixel AI to 11,111px.  
I color corrected in Photoshop Camera Raw on desktop.  
Then brought it back to the iPad Pro for 10 more hours of Procreate paint-over for final polish, detail, and charm.  
Original GAN image and Procreate Time-lapse videos available to owners through my website.

Abstract Art lives in the realm of the unknown and thrives with experimentation. This process of painting over a GAN was something I wanted to try the second I saw GAN art because I wasn't immediately comfortable minting it directly as my work. I'm happy with the results. I made it with pleasure.
